Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.88,0:08:05.80,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}えーと　日本語でいうと
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.24,0:08:06.89,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}梁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.05,0:08:08.89,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Yes exactly
