Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.88,0:10:11.10,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}立派なクライマーになれるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.76,0:10:12.44,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}よし
