Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.47,0:10:57.25,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}オッケー
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.45,0:11:00.46,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}しーちゃん　1回降ろすわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.46,0:11:01.59,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}はいにゃ
