Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.04,0:16:14.00,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}OK
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.76,0:16:17.17,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}ムーランルージュ
