Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.59,0:19:30.53,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}もう勉強しなきゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.72,0:19:31.82,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}ぷりん
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.41,0:19:34.24,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}おやすみ
