Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.47,0:10:57.25,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}OK
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.45,0:11:00.46,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}小希 先放下来
