Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.41,0:11:20.32,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}社长 专员
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.32,0:11:22.35,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}谢谢帮助
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.09,0:11:25.40,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不愧是专业人士的手法
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.40,0:11:27.00,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Good job
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.49,0:11:33.20,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}小事一桩
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.20,0:11:36.17,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}之后可能还要拜托加工木材
Dialogue: 1,0:11:36.36,0:11:38.34,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯 交给我们吧
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.87,0:11:42.68,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那么今天就到此为止
