Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.87,0:11:45.90,Dial_CH,,800,0,0,,{\blur4}喵
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.87,0:11:45.90,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}OK
Dialogue: 1,0:11:52.52,0:11:54.16,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}终于开始了
