Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.92,0:12:23.20,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}3000毫米 正好3米
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.16,0:12:40.73,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}给 塞璐芙
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.73,0:12:41.62,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.19,0:12:42.94,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}给你
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.49,0:12:44.35,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好的喵
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.22,0:12:56.20,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我回来了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.75,0:13:17.18,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}辛苦了
