Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.02,0:13:26.28,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}然后再去一下TREE吧
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.51,0:13:28.48,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}都成固定路线了呢
